☐ Add `babel.assumptions` config
   https://babeljs.io/assumptions
☐ Configure browser targets in Webpack's top-level `target` option:
   https://webpack.js.org/configuration/target/#browserslist
   browserslist:${browserslist query}
☐ Use webpack 5's new asset modules instead of url-loader and file-loader
   https://webpack.js.org/guides/asset-modules/
☐ Check if npm-install-plugin's approach still works in Webpack 5 and fix it if not